At Cleaning in action windows & more inc. 
Our services include:
- Window cleaning
- Gutter cleaning
- Pressure washing
- Carpet cleaning
- High level Dusting
- Christmas light installation and removal
- Cleaning services Move in/move out, Commercial, Post construction
We offer our services in Calgary and surrounding areas.
We are licensed, registered, insured and covered by workers compensation.
We show our work on our Instagram page cleaning_in_action 
For a free estimate call or text 403-796-2728 or email info@cleaninginaction.ca
